{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-plugin-stripe","description":"Gatsby plugin that adds stripe.js to site","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","stripe","stripe.js"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"njosefbeck","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/9f4a4690c7d0ff146a34c1787e801cfb"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/njosefbeck/gatsby-plugin-stripe"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-plugin-stripe\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-stripe\" aria-label=\"gatsby plugin stripe permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-plugin-stripe</h1>\n<p>A simple plugin that adds <code class=\"language-text\">stripe.js</code> to every page on your Gatsby site.</p>\n<p>This is especially useful for building out a Stripe integration using Stripe <a href=\"https://stripe.com/docs/elements\">Elements</a> or the new version of Stripe Checkout (now in beta).</p>\n<p>If you’re using Stripe Elements, once <code class=\"language-text\">stripe.js</code> is added to your Gatsby site, you can use <a href=\"https://github.com/stripe/react-stripe-elements\">Stripe’s React Element components</a> to integrate Elements into your site.</p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-label=\"how to use permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Install using either npm or yarn:</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn add gatsby-plugin-stripe</code></pre></div>\n<p>or</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install gatsby-plugin-stripe</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Add to <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code></li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-stripe`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>To load the <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;script&gt;</code> tag asyncronously, pass an ‘async’ option in <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-stripe`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">async</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-plugin-stripe/","id":"2aef7030-4a9c-5f68-b1b6-744d1a8637d1","layout":"plugins"}}